{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/carrinho_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">LE FOL is a visual experience inspired by the Fool\u2019s Journey, a point-and-click, multiple ending narrative game, full of puzzles and poetry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/jornada_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world that mixes reality with the Tarot universe, the protagonist, apathetic and disconnected from life itself, goes on an intense journey of self-knowledge through the Major Arcana, which represents a specific aspect of LE FOL's life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/arstyle.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With an unique 2D isometric visual style, inspired by analog art and impressionist movements, explore the contrast between the density and solidness of S\u00e3o Paulo and the fluidity of the natural world, which creates a setting that is simultaneously challenging and welcoming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/puzzles_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout your journey, solve thematic puzzles associated with each Arcana, creating, combining and organizing objects and solving the problems presented to LE FOL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/personaliza\u00e7\u00e3o_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Express yourself through the character and Diary customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/poesia_en.png?t=1738718519\" />Like a howl to space and the absolute void, like a voice that doesn't come out, LE FOL uses its own poetry as a way of expressing themself to the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738718519","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/page.bg.jpg?t=1738718519","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/befe9b51098702a1656e895635a62f0289e2b946/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738718519","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/befe9b51098702a1656e895635a62f0289e2b946/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738718519","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":"This game could be a trigger for people because, through the poetry and artwork's subjectiveness, it talks about sensitive subjects, such as homophobia, transphobia, self-harm, substance abuse, and depression. The intention of this title is to discuss these heavy themes through the character lens and their poetry."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/carrinho_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">LE FOL is a visual experience inspired by the Fool\u2019s Journey, a point-and-click, multiple ending narrative game, full of puzzles and poetry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/jornada_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world that mixes reality with the Tarot universe, the protagonist, apathetic and disconnected from life itself, goes on an intense journey of self-knowledge through the Major Arcana, which represents a specific aspect of LE FOL's life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/arstyle.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With an unique 2D isometric visual style, inspired by analog art and impressionist movements, explore the contrast between the density and solidness of S\u00e3o Paulo and the fluidity of the natural world, which creates a setting that is simultaneously challenging and welcoming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/puzzles_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout your journey, solve thematic puzzles associated with each Arcana, creating, combining and organizing objects and solving the problems presented to LE FOL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/personaliza\u00e7\u00e3o_en.png?t=1738718519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Express yourself through the character and Diary customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/extras/poesia_en.png?t=1738718519\" />Like a howl to space and the absolute void, like a voice that doesn't come out, LE FOL uses its own poetry as a way of expressing themself to the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["zagoiris"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472140/header.jpg?t=1738718519","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257092550,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257092550/mov